        "oni (m animate)": "byli by dělali",
        "ony (f/inanimate)": "byly by dělaly"
      },
      "notes": "Past conditional = past tense of být (byl bych...) + L-participle of main verb. Rare in spoken Czech; used in literature and hypothetical past.",
